  "title": "Retail Admin Assistant | Up to $2200",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />We are looking for a responsible and detail-oriented <strong>Retail Admin Assistant</strong> to support daily administrative operations at our retail stores. The role requires strong organizational skills, accuracy in documentation, and the ability to work effectively in a fast-paced environment.<br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Monday to Friday</p></li><li><p><strong>10.45am to 8.30pm</strong><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Work Location:</strong></p><ul><li><p>VivoCity / Causeway Point / Town area<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Gross monthly salary: $2,000 – $2,200</strong><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform general <strong>administrative duties</strong> to support store operations.</p></li><li><p>Process <strong>SAP-related documents</strong>, including invoice verification, goods receipt, data entry, and document filing.</p></li><li><p>Handle incoming phone calls and manage basic office administrative matters.</p></li><li><p>Monitor and replenish <strong>office and housekeeping supplies</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Assist in <strong>stocktaking activities</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Carry out any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Retail Manager.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>O-Level qualification</strong> with at least <strong>2 years of relevant experience</strong>, preferably in <strong>retail or hospitality</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in <strong>Microsoft Office</strong> (Word and Excel).</p></li><li><p>Good <strong>communication and interpersonal skills</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Able to work well in a <strong>fast-paced environment</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Able to <strong>commence work immediately or within short notice</strong>.</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong><br />📩 <strong>Apply Now</strong></p><p>Send your resume (MS Word format) to:</p><p>📱 WhatsApp / Telegram: 8509 0409</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary in your application.</p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>—</p><p>Annie Hoang (R25158747)</p><p>CREW by HRnet |HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd </p><p>EA24C2435</p>",
